<div class="text-center">
<h2>Some keynotes before you start..</h2>

  <p>You will have 60 seconds to respond each one of the questions</p>
  <p>There are 4 possible answers, only 1 is the correct one</p>
  <p>Once responded, you can take as much time to go to the next question</p>
  <p>Once you fail to respond a question, you will need to wait 30 minutes to try again</p>
  <p>The project is on Alpha, so expect some flaws</p>
</div>

<div class="index-action-container text-center">
  {{#if gameFinished}}
    <h4>Come back in ~30 minutes to try again</h4>
  {{/if}}
  {{#link-to "game" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg"}}
    {{#if gameInProgress}}
      Continue Game
    {{else if gameFinished}}
      View Scoreboard
    {{else}}
      Start Game
    {{/if}}
  {{/link-to}}
</div>
